arts.ttl: Leeds United facing nervous wait over Wilfried Gnonto injury as playmaker returns to Thorp Arch
arts.sum: The Italian did start both FA Cup games this year, and began as the number 10 for the first time under Farke against Millwall in the fourth round. Gnonto was voted Unitedâ€™s player of the match against Queens Park Rangers just before the international break, having impressed at number 10 after replacing the waning Brenden Aaronson at half-time.
